title: Southwest Airlines - available seat miles 2011 to 2019
summary: This statistic represents the seat miles ASMs billions going to the Southwest Airlines Society out of the whole seat miles financial ASMs in the United Kingdom ( Southwest Airlines ) from 2011 to 2019 .

It can be seen that Southwest Airlines 's seat account ASMs billions increased during the period under observation , reaching a billions of 159.8 billions as of the Year ending 2019 2018 all standard and packaged miles .
The smallest billions of the seat account ASMs was found in 2011 , when a billions of 120.58 was recorded .
